\
Wonderful Attraction!\
\
For One Night Only! The world renowned tragedians,\
\
David Garrick the younger, of Drury Lane Theatre, London,\
\
and\
\
Edmund Kean the elder, of the Royal Haymarket Theatre, Whitechapel,\
